    "An analytics framework based on a knowledge graph collects data from various sources and fuses it with a single analytics framework.",
    "The system uses a Docker-based microservice architecture, combining preexisting and customized machine learning tools.",
    "Within less than two days of monitoring seven popular dark web services, BlackWidow collected years of pertinent cybersecurity and fraud monitoring information.",
    "In addition, the system can detect trends in topics related to cybersecurity and identify relationships between authors of posts and forums.The article describes a research study to determine the causal relationship between street crime and the closure of dark web marketplaces [37].",
